Get the best payment processing
for any business

From retail and restaurants, to eCommerce and
education—and everything in between—we offer
the best payment services in Los Angeles.
Free Quote
Contact Sales

Payments for All Business Types

If you need to accept debit, credit, or other payment types, we offer the solution for your business.

Retail

Accept payments in person with our secure terminals.

Resturant

Everything you need, from credit card terminals to complete POS software.

Food Trucks

Make your payment processing as flexible as you are.

E-Commerce

Supercharge your shopping cart.

Automotive Service / Repair

Expand your payment options.

SME businesses

Grow your business with our simple and secure payment options.

B2B Businesses

From portals to automated invoicing, we make collecting payments easy.

NonProfits

Take donations online, in person, over the phone, or anywhere else you may be.

Dentists

Take payments, manage payments, and more.

Healthcare / Medical

Accept payments while staying HIPAA and PCI-compliant.

Lawyers / Legal

Invoice your clients for hassle-free payments.

Churches

Donations are now easier than ever.

Contractors

Send invoices, take payments in the field, and more.

Government Agencies

Get low rates for government agencies.

Craft Vendors

Take payments on the go at fairs and festivals.

Cryptocurrencies

Start accepting cryptocurrency payments, like Bitcoin, today.

Dating Sites

Set up recurring payments for your subscribers.

Dispensaries

Process payments using PIN debit, eCheck, crypto, and more.

SAAS Companies

Sell your software subscriptions online with maximum security.

Schools / Education Centers

Manage payments through the most common education software.

Travel Agencies

Get advanced fraud detection for your high-ticket transactions.

Gas Stations

Low rates, fast payouts, and advanced fraud protection.

Photographers

Accept payments on your website and on your phone.

Home Improvement

The perfect payment options for plumbers, electricians, and HVAC companies.

Hospitality

Expertly manage authorizations, payments, and chargebacks.

Golf Courses & Sports

Get POS systems tailor-made especially for you.

Liquor & Wine Store

Manage your sales, age verification, and inventory with our POS systems.

Clothing & Accessories

Sell online or in a retail store, all with our powerful POS.

Spa & Salons

Our POS systems feature online self-booking, loyalty programs, and more.

Websites

Accept payments on your website with cutting edge security options.

Therapists

Expand your virtual payment options.

Vacation Rentals

Manage deposits, bookings, and payments with specialized POS systems.

Accountants

Integrate with your existing accounting software.

Bars

Manage payments, schedules, and inventory with our POS systems.

Bookstores

Take payments through your existing POS and eCommerce systems.

Car Dealerships

Accept all types of payments while managing details across your departments.

Best Merchant Processing Services In Los Angeles.

Our banking and technology partners

Transform your
idea into an app
with our experts.

Let our experts create a mobile app specifically for your business and start selling directly to your customers
